		<div class="bCommentText">
		Here's mine.  I did not make this from scratch.  I think I found parts of it in the FAQ or mailing list, the modified it:<br />
<br />
# Change scrollback to 10000 lines<br />
defscrollback 10000<br />
<br />
# status line at the bottom<br />
hardstatus on<br />
hardstatus alwayslastline<br />
hardstatus string "%{.bW}%-w%{.rW}%f%n %t%{-}%+w %=%{..G}[%H %l] %{..Y} %m/%d %c "<br />
<br />
http://directedge.us/content/screenrc-file<br />
<br />
-orev	</div>
